thread.title: Sam

author: Sam
title: Sam
text: After reading different companies claims I was originally going to try Red Monkey from Red Supplements. It was out of stick so I bought phenibut caps from liftmode. I was not disappointed! When I ran out Red Monkey was back in stock. I gave it a go because it had other things combined with the phenibut. I WAS disappointed! I have since ordered more phenibut from liftmode. Always fast shipping!
